# Website UI/UX Evaluation & Recommendations

This report evaluates the website running on `localhost:5173`, focusing on visibility, color schemes, interactive elements, and overall usability.

> [!NOTE]
> The evaluation was performed on the active local development server. An automated browser session reviewed the pages and interactions.

![Website UI Review Recording](C:/Users/chase/.gemini/antigravity/brain/111e353d-0e8a-4ca0-8ff9-f2ce09e9c38d/website_ui_review_1771884560849.webp)

## 1. Visual Design & Layout

- **Aesthetic:** The website employs a high-end, minimalist aesthetic that feels both modern and empathetic. It uses generous amounts of whitespace (padding and margins) to create a "breathable" experience, which aligns perfectly with a relationship coaching brand.
- **Typography:** The site uses a sophisticated pairing of an elegant serif font (featuring dramatic italics in menus) and a clean geometric sans-serif (e.g., *Outfit*). This contrast successfully communicates both emotional depth and professional clarity.
- **Layout Structure:** Content is organized in clearly defined sections using centered hero components and grid-based feature cards. The transition between sections is smooth, aided by subtle animations and scroll indicators.

